核醣核酸生物學
研究主要探討核醣核酸剪接反應，降解，非編碼核酸之調控以及核酸相關引發的疾病的機制。


核醣核酸生物學方面的研究人員:

陳俊安 Chen, Jun-An Non-coding RNA Function during Motor Neuron Development and Degeneration
鄭淑珍 Cheng, Soo-Chen Molecular mechanism of pre-mRNA splicing
林淑端 Lin-Chao, Sue Cell Growth Control: I. RNA decay and bacterial cell growth. II. Mammalian growth arrest genes
沈哲鯤 Shen, Che-Kun James Eukaryotic Gene Regulation and Development
吳惠南 Wu, Huey-Nan RNA Protein Interactions in RNA Viruses
姚孟肇 Yao, Meng-Chao Gene Amplification, DNA Rearrangements and Chromosome Instability in Eukaryotes
袁小琀 Yuan, Hanna Structural and Functional Studies of RNA and DNA Metabolism







